name: MUNI
description: $Muni has a vision to kick start meme season 2.0 by bringing real, audited utility to you, the investor. We are built by you and for you. We understand that money is what we’re here for and $Muni is what we’ll get. Its time to make some $Muni again. The heart and soul of Muni’s purpose is to provide safe and effective bear market utility. Our primary focus is on the safety of the project and safety of the money invested into us by you. Muni has developed its very own telegram bot, capable of overtaking some of the largest competitors. Functions within the bot allow the user to look at price stats, various chart timeframes, liquidity, and other unique features like a honeypot checker, all on telegram. MuniBot can be used by all users and is ready to be mass adopted. MuniBot will allow users to access the utility of honeypot.is, Dextools and others all from the comforts of your Telegram chats. There is no need to have 10 different tabs open for one coin anymore.
